{
  "message": "fix: min_cost_flow demand convention and conformance fixture corrections\n\nFix min_cost_flow to properly handle NetworkX demand convention where\nnegative = supply and positive = demand. The internal algorithm was\nusing the opposite convention, causing incorrect flow computations.\n\nAlso fix conformance fixtures:\n- Replace invalid bellman_ford_negative_weights_strict.json with\n  bellman_ford_weighted_path_strict.json (undirected graphs with\n  negative weights always have negative cycles)\n- Fix global_edge_connectivity_k4_strict.json field name\n- Add dijkstra_diamond_weighted and triangles_k4 conformance tests\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
